===Verb===
# To block light or radio transmission.
#: ''We're shadowed by that cloud.''
# To secretly track or follow another, to keep under [[surveillance]].
# {{complang}} To make an [[identifier]], usually a variable, inaccessable by declaring another of the same name within the [[scope]] of the first.

